  "body": "<p>Hope you all enjoyed Plus One week on the American Crafts blog. There were so many wonderful projects - love how the same products can be interpreted into many different ways. Here's a little re-cap in case you missed it.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599040159080-Z5UF88I3BK57RKOOYQH6/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Monday - Layouts by Ashley Horton<br/>Tuesday - Mini Album Tutorial by Becki Adams <br/>Wednesday - Guest Designer Jen Chesnick <br/>Thursday - Cards by Patricia Roebuck <br/>Friday - Layout &amp; Card by Elizabeth Gardner </p><p>We're hitting the road in a couple hours for San Diego to teach my first class using Plus One items (available at local stores and online at <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DAmy%2DTangerine%2DPlus%2DOne%2FCategories\">Simon Says Stamp</a> and Two Peas In A Bucket.) Hope you all have a wonderful weekend!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}